data.description: Welcome to your dream ranch-style home, nestled near the historic charm of Bardstown. This meticulously maintained property offers a perfect blend of elegance and comfort. With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a wealth of other features, it's time to turn your dreams of rural living into a reality. Upon entering, you'll be immediately captivated by the rich atmosphere of the home. Two whirlpool tubs and standalone showers ensure your personal sanctuary for relaxation. The master bedroom, adorned with French doors, offers a private escape onto the deck. Picture yourself sipping your morning coffee while being serenaded by the gentle rustling of leaves or enjoying a morning sunrise in the sunroom. The open concept living area creates an inviting and flexible space, with two generously sized areas adjacent to the kitchen, perfect for hosting friends and family. Whether it's a cozy night by the fireplace or a grand celebration, this home adapts to your every need. Newly updated hardwood and ceramic tile flooring adds a touch of modern sophistication throughout. The quality and craftsmanship are unmistakable, promising comfort and durability for years to come. This home is also practical. Equipped with a 500-gallon in-ground propane tank and a reliable backup generator, you'll be prepared for any eventuality. Your comfort and security are top priorities. The sweltering summer months are no match for the in-ground saltwater pool, complete with a diving board on the 8-ft deep end. As you cool off in its crystal-clear waters, you'll appreciate the ambiance created by the black wrought iron fencing and meticulous landscaping that surrounds the pool. Your four-legged friends haven't been forgotten. A 10x16 Amish shed/dog house with flooring and A/C, enclosed by bar and chain-length fencing, ensures your pets are comfortable and safe. Hobbies, vehicles, and toys all have their place in the spacious detached garage. Whether you're a collector or an adventurer, you'll find ample room to house your treasures. Spanning just over 20 acres, this property opens up a world of possibilities. A large, fully stocked pond awaits, teeming with bass and catfish. Whether you're a seasoned angler or just looking for moments of tranquility, this oasis in the country has it all. Wildlife enthusiasts will delight in the opportunity to observe the local wildlife in their natural habitat. This is your chance to embrace the serene beauty of rural living, all while enjoying the finest comforts.
